My work will be exhibiting in the Shades of Compassion exhibition alongside artists such as Ansel Adams, Imogen Cunningham, Jerry N. Uelsmann, and 40 other renowned photographers worldwide. 
This is a traveling exhibition and the work will be shown in Headley-Whitney Museum of Art April 8-June 18th. 

I'm very honoured to be exhibiting among such big names. If you're checking out the show, do send me pictures. 
Thank you for continuing to follow and support my work. 

